{"tid":2131694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中美角力】中銀證券發報告籲中國需為美國制裁作準備，或以CIPS取代SWIFT","createTime":"2020-07-30T04:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T07:53:09.000Z","uid":51665,"like":79,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"4a663beb8525a38d9aeb4b3b20f352dd04cdee68","tid":2131694,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/560680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F560680&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=0f124ca5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/560680</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/XTNC-990x520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2FXTNC-990x520.jpg&h=b5d42354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《路透社》報道，中國銀行旗下的投資銀行&mdash;中銀證券發表報告指，中國應加強自己與港澳的跨境交易金融網絡，以防美國對個別中資銀行的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n報告由中銀證券與前外匯監管機構共同撰寫，目的是針對美國近期就是否將中國從環球同業銀行金融電訊協會(SWIFT)剔除而發表，它提到：「敵人向你打出漂亮的一拳，可以令你迴避到接下來的一百拳。」(A good punch to the enemy will save yourself from hundreds of punches from your enemies.)， 報告指考慮了到兩國關係逐漸惡化，所以要思考下一步。<br />\n報告提到中國應以自家的中國跨境銀行間支付系統(CIPS)，取代比利時的SIWFT，以減少中國將交易數據的曝光在美國眼前，在必要時，中國更應考慮停止使用美元作為其外匯管制的主要貨幣，及制訂頒佈類似歐盟的「阻斷法」，在特殊情形下考慮外匯調控及貨幣換錨等宏觀層面措施。在微觀層面上，北京需加強監測輿論並制定應對預案，加大反洗錢力度，維護和發展海外非美元清算行代理行關係，引導境內企業減少美元計價結算等。SWIFT是國際銀行間的國際合作組織，組織包含全球大多數國家銀行。SWIFT提供安全、可靠、快捷、自動化的通訊業務，從而大大提高了銀行的結算速度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n報告預測美國有機會採取來對抗中國的手段，包括切斷中國在SWIFT的訊息權限，從而切斷中國的國際金融網絡。而美國落實的《香港自治法案》中提到，將禁止部分中港官員在美國管轄範圍與金融機構進行信用轉讓或支付，而中國則可以利用CIPS禁止美國人投資或購買相關機構的股權和債券，參與美國金融系統進行交易等。<br />\n<br />\n中國於2015年啟動CIPS結算系統，助人民幣國際化。在中央銀行的監督下，CIPS表示，2019年每天處理1,357億元人民幣，有96個國家和地區參與。<br />\n<br />\n班港奸仲要掛美元到幾時呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7cbc04a846643d824648f5748536cf749f58ca","tid":2131694,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:26:03.000Z","msg":"內循環"},{"pid":"e8eda4ddf81351c83400caf1d7cdf458bd245679","tid":2131694,"uid":36359,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"「敵人向你打出漂亮的一拳，可以令你迴避到接下來的一百拳。」(A good punch to the enemy will save yourself from hundreds of punches from your enemies.)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d402d7249e2a3d282a414f773d717f115376b7a8","tid":2131694,"uid":176313,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"維尼呢兩日亞投行會議就係諗呢啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3345284fecb38ecb69cd0bd382a1dfacf8dd65f6","tid":2131694,"uid":6639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8eda4ddf81351c83400caf1d7cdf458bd245679","tid":2131694,"uid":36359,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"「敵人向你打出漂亮的一拳，可以令你迴避到接下來的一百拳。」(A good punch to the enemy will save yourself from hundreds of punches from your enemies.)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3424fcc33bbafce2c8921737c6c33219afef3739","tid":2131694,"uid":40839,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"e8eda4ddf81351c83400caf1d7cdf458bd245679","tid":2131694,"uid":36359,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"「敵人向你打出漂亮的一拳，可以令你迴避到接下來的一百拳。」(A good punch to the enemy will save yourself from hundreds of punches from your e